      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "8efc3d770c13e4a0",
      "text": "**How do you allow individual business units to make progress without imposing overhead for coordination?**\n   \n   Empowering individual business units while minimizing coordination overhead requires a [[Balance of Autonomy and Alignment]]. Establishing clear goals and guidelines, promoting open communication channels, and fostering a culture of collaboration can help facilitate progress without excessive coordination burdens. Additionally, implementing modular or microservices-based architectures can allow for more independent development and deployment by business units while still ensuring interoperability and consistency."
